    text: "Root-cause provenance: the new event is from an external media-server pm-ops consumer on Node v22.19.0 and published pm-cli 2026.7.13. This checkout runs on mainframe with Node v26.4.0. The event is pre-fix external-consumer traffic, not current-head capture; publication of this PR carries the typed CommandError suppression forward."
