    text: "Live closeout: resolved Sentry issue 124400835 after proving event provenance from the external pre-fix media-server consumer. Rerun sentry-telemetry-gate passed with critical=0, high=0, ignored expected handled=16, finish_error_rate_pct=0.27, and failures_without_error_code_rows=0."
  - created_at: "2026-07-14T02:41:12.182Z"
    author: codex-root
    text: "Security remediation: release secret-scan correctly rejected a host-specific absolute path in the Sentry provenance comment. Replacing it with a host-neutral external pm-ops consumer label across current metadata and history."
  - created_at: "2026-07-14T02:41:45.151Z"
    author: codex-root
    text: "Security closeout: edited the provenance comment to host-neutral wording, then history-redact replaced the absolute path across the full stream. check-secrets reports no credential-like secrets; history verification reports 29 entries, verify_ok=true, and current_matches_latest=true."
